description:
On today’s show, Emily is talking about some things that most relationships go through and how to get past them.

She goes over the top things couples argue about and ways to deal with them, why you shouldn’t let kissing slip from your relationship, and how to make sure you’re both getting your needs met in the bedroom – because sex is a two-way street. Plus, how to to let your partner know gently that they need to work on their oral hygiene.
